## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online sources, which may not cover all perspectives or the latest developments in animal rights discourse. Additionally, the ethical and philosophical nature of the topic means that conclusions are often subjective and influenced by personal beliefs and cultural contexts. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.

